page 60: "-What?" Yea that's my reaction to all these harem power fantasy convenient hentai where everythings goes 100% smoothly for the mc, oh well, at least it's not the typical japanese isekai'd main character "nihonsuke" which may or may not be the author himself, for once. I do notice that these are so "samey" that the patterns these hentai works follow are all the same down to the order in which the harem mc gets its bitches, first the elf, then then the queen (often rolled into one) then the dragonoid, then the furry (dragon = scales, no furr. furry humanoid is usually a bunny/cat/dog girl, may appear before the dragonoid), followed by the angel/android/demon/elemental/monster girl (which is usually the first if there are no elves in the plot) and last but not least, the, rather plain by comparison, childhood friend who's sort of, just there until the harem mc feels like putting his dick in it as well.
